Hi
> You may be thinking of an I2C interface, not I2O.  I2C is used to
> control TV tuners and other such devices.
On the subject of the I2C interface, is there some work being done to
produce a single, unified I2C module? Right now, I can't watch TV and
monitor my PC as bttv and the lm_sensors package have their own I2C
drivers which are mutually incompatible (and cause a mild oops when
run together).
